{"article_id":"HfPO496ldm2dBNf3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama and top campaign staffers made clear this weekend","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"they will not apologize","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"for saying","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"the financial company Bain Capital outsourced jobs under Mitt Romney ' s leadership","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and suggesting","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Romney may have committed a felony with his SEC filings .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"The president addressed the issue during an interview Saturday with WAVY-TV in Virginia .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"The station is scheduled to air the interview Sunday night ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"but it can be seen now on WAVY ' s website .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" We won ' t be apologizing , \"","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Obama said .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"\" Mr . Romney claims","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"he 's Mr. Fix-It for the economy","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"because of his business experience ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"so I think","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"voters entirely , legitimately want to know","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"what is exactly his business experience . ''","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The question did not directly address Romney ' s call Friday for an apology","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"after Obama deputy campaign manager Stephanie Cutter suggested","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that Romney in Securities and Exchange Commission filings misrepresented his position at Bain Capital ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"particularly when he officially left ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"which","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"she said","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"would either be a \" felony \" or a misrepresentation to Americans .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"But Cutter was clear","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"when asked about that remark Sunday .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"\" He ' s not going to get an apology , \"","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Cutter said Sunday of CBS ' \" Face the Nation . \"","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Cutter 's faced off on the show with Romney campaign adviser Kevin Madden ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"he was troubled by the fact","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" the president would direct his campaign to label someone like Romney ... as a felon . \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"He also said","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"news agency fact-checkers have repeatedly found","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that records accurately show","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"his candidate left Bain in 1999 .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"\" Yet the Obama campaign and even the president himself continue to pursue these inaccurate statements , \"","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Madden said .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Though Cutter stood by her comments on Romney ,","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"top Obama campaign adviser David Axelrod earlier in the day attempted to clarify the remarks .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"\" She didn ' t say","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"he ' s a felon , \"","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Axelrod said on CNN ' s \" State of the Union . \"","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Romney on Friday also challenged Obama to `` rein in '' his campaign team","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"and called the comment `` absurd '' and `` beneath the dignity of the presidency . ''","depth":3},{"id":45,"text":"During the TV interview , the president also tried to deflect criticism","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"that he has attacked the Republican candidate","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"for running a firm","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"that made money","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"and created jobs .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"`` As the head of a private equity firm , [ Romney ' s ] job was to maximize profits","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"and help investors , \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Obama said .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"\" There is nothing wrong with that .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"On the other hand , that company also was investing in companies","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that were called by The Washington Post 'the pioneers of outsourcing . '","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Mr. Romney is now claiming","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"he was n't there at the time","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"except his filings with the SEC listing says","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"he was the CEO , chairman and president of the company . \"","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"During a campaign stop in Virginia , the president continued his attack on Romney and Bain ,","depth":4},{"id":61,"text":"saying ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"\" I don ' t want a pioneer in outsourcing .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"I want some in-sourcing .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"I want to bring companies back . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":129,"left":107,"right":128,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":81,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":73,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":70,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":0,"right":69,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":1,"right":68,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":66,"right":67,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":66,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":6,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":74,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":76,"right":78,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":11,"right":75,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left"